name: VOYEUR
description: Endless windows tell endless stories, like stacks of televisions. And despite what people try to portray, we are all curious about: the widow with her quirky collections, the cat that just wants out, the exhibitionist, the nice couple that fights ALL the time, and the man with the gun. They all lead their own unique and mysterious tales, and we are always ready to watch.- model: Kat Hall - body paint and photography by Roustan (bodypainter.com)
